init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's not used to being rejected.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: interested in a relationship with a man who's always changing into a different man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man has a good friend who is a witch.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells him that he can change the woman into a shapeshifter just like him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells him it is a good thing to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: goes home and makes the tea.

actions.name: text-insert
